      "Standard": "ASHRAE 55-2020",
      "Category": "Temperature",
      "Description": "Thermal Environmental Conditions for Human Occupancy",
      "Requirement": "Indoor operative temperature must be maintained within 67°F-82°F (19.4°C-27.8°C) for occupied spaces during business hours",
